<div dir="ltr">IIRC it was not possible to merge with a dirty tree with git 1.7.<div>So, Dave, you may have been bitten in those dark days.</div><div>-Paul</div></div><div class="gmail_extra"><br><div class="gmail_quote">On Mon, Nov 3, 2014 at 8:49 AM, Dave Goodell (dgoodell) <span dir="ltr">&lt;<a href="mailto:dgoodell@cisco.com" target="_blank">dgoodell@cisco.com</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br><blockquote class="gmail_quote" style="margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex"><div class="HOEnZb"><div class="h5">On Nov 3, 2014, at 10:41 AM, Jed Brown &lt;<a href="mailto:jed@jedbrown.org">jed@jedbrown.org</a>&gt; wrote:<br>
